com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.queue.models

Class PeekMessagesResult.QueueMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.queue.models.PeekMessagesResult.QueueMessage
  • Enclosing class:
    PeekMessagesResult

    public static class PeekMessagesResult.QueueMessage
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a message in the queue returned by the server. A PeekMessagesResult.QueueMessage instance contains a copy of the queue message data in the storage service as of the time the message was requested.
